resource.title: Treatment plan for liver cirrhosis
resource.description: Comprehensive treatment plan including Liver Transplant Evaluation, Liver Transplant Surgery, Post-transplant Follow-up

resource.conclusion: Patient shows improving status for liver cirrhosis. Sakura Nguyen, a 46-year-old Asian female with severe liver cirrhosis underwent successful liver transplant surgery on March 15, 2022. Post-transplant recovery is progressing well with close monitoring and immunosuppressant therapy.
